AUTHOR: Vusi Ka-Caleni
DATE: April 2015

How to play:

	Controls: 
		Keyboard:
			Spacebar = Fire lazer
			F = Fire Missile
			P = Pause game
			Arrow keys = Movement
		PS3 Controller:
			X = Fire lazer
			R1 = Fire lazer
			Circle = Fire Missile
			Start = Pause game
			Analog sticks = Movement

Object of the game:
Kill all the enemies! Good luck!